<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2731/1999 of 21 December 1999 amending Regulation (EC) No 2603/97 laying down the detailed implementing rules for imports of rice originating in the ACP countries or the overseas countries and territories (OCT) </inglise>
