<inglise> Having regard to Council Decision 91/482/EEC of 25 July 1991 on the association of the overseas countries and territories with the European Economic Community(1), as last amended by Decision 97/803/EC(2), and in particular Article 108a(5) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. juuli 1991. aasta otsust 91/482/EM&Uuml; &uuml;lemeremaade ja -territooriumide assotsieerimise kohta Euroopa Majandus&uuml;hendusega, (1) viimati muudetud otsusega 97/803/E&Uuml;, (2) eriti selle artikli 108a l&otilde;iget 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 1706/98 of 20 July 1998 on the arrangements applicable to agricultural products and goods resulting from the processing of agricultural products originating in the African, Caribbean and Pacific States (ACP) and repealing Regulation (EEC) No 715/90(3), and in particular Article 30(1) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 20. juuli 1998. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 1706/98 Aafrika, Kariibi mere ja Vaikse ookeani piirkonna riikidest (AKV riikidest) p&auml;rit p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel saadud p&otilde;llumajandustoodete ja kaupade suhtes kohaldatava korra kohta ning m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 715/90 kehtetuks tunnistamise kohta, (3) eriti selle artikli 30 l&otilde;iget 1, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Article 9(3) of Regulation (EC) No 2603/97 allows operators to withdraw applications for licences where a reduction percentage is applied. In the light of experience, there are grounds for limiting withdrawal of applications to cases where the application of a reduction percentage would result in the issue of an import licence for a quantity that is not economically viable. </inglise>
<eesti> 2) m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2603/97 artikli 9 l&otilde;ige 3 v&otilde;imaldab ettev&otilde;tjatel litsentsitaotlusi tagasi v&otilde;tta juhtudel, kui kohaldatakse v&auml;hendusprotsenti; kogemust silmas pidades on p&otilde;hjendatud litsentside tagasiv&otilde;tmise piiramine juhtudele, kui v&auml;hendusprotsendi kohaldamine tooks kaasa impordilitsentside v&auml;ljaandmise koguse kohta, mis ei ole majanduslikult tasuv; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) The measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for cereals, </inglise>
